2. Interpretation
In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires—
"borehole" means a well sunk by means of a rig or machinery, and shall not include a well sunk by persons subject to any Botswana customary law, with hand labour only, in any of the tribal territories defined in the Tribal Territories Act (Cap. 32:03) or on any of the Barolong Farms;
